# Internal communications

Use terse, evidence-first updates for routine handoffs:

```text
FINDING: ...
EVIDENCE: path:line or command output
RISK: green | yellow | red
FIX: ...
VERIFY: exact command
```

Never compress: user requirements, security requirements, API contracts, migrations, exact errors, code, commands, file paths, acceptance criteria.

Architect format: MISSION, STATE, PLAN, SCOPE, VERIFY, RISKS, HANDOFF.
